{{EngvarB|date=November 2015}} {{Use dmy dates|date=November 2015}} {{Infobox government agency | agency_name =National Board for Technical Education | type =Board | logo =NBTE logo.jpeg | logo_width =148px | logo_caption = | formed =1977 | preceding1 = | preceding2 = | dissolved = | superseding1 =[[Nigerian Federal Ministry of Education]] | agency_type = | jurisdiction =[[Federal Government of Nigeria]] | headquarters =[[Kaduna]], [[Kaduna State]], Nigeria | coordinates = | motto =Education for Self Reliance | employees = | budget = | chief1_name = | chief1_position = | public_protector = | deputy = | parent_department = | parent_agency = | child1_agency = | website = {{URL|nbte.gov.ng/}} | footnotes = | embed = }}
The '''National Board for Technical Education''', otherwise known as NBTE, is a [[board of education]] which supervises, regulates and oversee educational programmes offered by technical institutions at secondary, [[Institute of technology|polytechnic]] and monotechnic levels through an accreditation process.<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.businessdayonline.com/2015/09/nigeria-has-no-clear-regulation-guiding-private-security/ | title=‘Nigeria has no clear regulation guiding private security’ | work=[[Business Day (Nigeria)|BusinessDay]] | date=12 September 2015 | accessdate=12 September 2015 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914002758/http://businessdayonline.com/2015/09/nigeria-has-no-clear-regulation-guiding-private-security/ | archivedate=14 September 2015 | df=dmy-all }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.thenationonlineng.net/key-into-buharis-anti-corruption-crusade-nbte-urges/ | title=Key into Buhari’s anti-corruption crusade, NBTE urges | work=[[The Nation (Nigeria)|The Nation]] | date=19 August 2015 | accessdate=12 September 2015}}</ref> It was established by Act No 9 of 11 July 1977 with the aim of "providing standardised minimum guide curricula for Technical and Vocational Education and Training".<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nbte.gov.ng/history.html | title=BRIEF HISTORY OF NATIONAL BOARD FOR TECHNICAL EDUCATION (NBTE) | publisher=National Board for Technical Education | accessdate=12 September 2015}}</ref>
